Structure in c++ are similar like classes.

C	C++
Only data members are allowed.	Can hold both data member and member function
It cannot have member function
Cannot have static member 	Can have static member
Cannot have constructor inside structure	Can have constructor inside structure
Direct initialisation of structure member is not allowed	Direct initialisation of structure member is allowed
Do not have access modifiers 	Can have access modifiers
Sizeof() operator will produce 0 for empty structure	Sizeof() operator will produce 1 for empty structure 





















